{"tid":2329324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★回血？】創科局長薛永恒1750萬元購大圍瑞峰花園　另兩高官同買樓","createTime":"2020-12-17T07:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T13:51:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cac98106d0c875a754da185fe2120bbe6d8bc3be","tid":2329324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201216/415985183175479296743512.jpeg/OUZ1z1zEPN28O1S9cJ3t4vLAqE_tZnRysF-mXrBfpl4?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201216%2F415985183175479296743512.jpeg%2FOUZ1z1zEPN28O1S9cJ3t4vLAqE_tZnRysF-mXrBfpl4%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=be470dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創科局局長薛永恒上月中申報其家人購買一個沙田單位，但未有透露詳情，《香港01》發現，其家人購入的是大圍瑞峰花園一個自住單位連一車位，作價1,750萬元。薛是今年迄今，申報入市的最高級官員，亦是繼發展局副局長廖振新後，第二位於施政報告宣讀前入市的政治委任官員，而兩位官員同於10月底入市。另外，發展局副秘書長上月初斥資2,600多萬元，以首置購入西半山單位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/562575/%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E8%96%9B%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%92%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%821750%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%BC%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E7%91%9E%E5%B3%B0%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92-%E5%8F%A6%E5%85%A9%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E5%90%8C%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%259F%25A5%2F562575%2F%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2596%259B%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%2581%2592%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B8%25821750%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592-%25E5%258F%25A6%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E6%25A8%2593&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28f%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=9f247130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/562575/%E5%89%B5%E7%A7%91%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%E8%96%9B%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%92%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%821750%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E8%B3%BC%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E7%91%9E%E5%B3%B0%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92-%E5%8F%A6%E5%85%A9%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E5%90%8C%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93</a><br />\n<br />\n本年4月22日獲委任創新及科技局局長的薛永恒，於上月17日向行政會議秘書處申報：「一個位於沙田區的住宅單位，由我的家庭成員擁有單位的100%業權，作自住用途」。"},{"pid":"6a70fa03f276dc2b35eb2ad052f70492d134616b","tid":2329324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"發展局副局長廖振新 首置購馬鞍山銀湖&middot;天峰<br />\n<br />\n早於薛的家人簽臨約的前兩日，即10月28日，發展局副局長廖振新亦在沙田區置業，以2,335萬元，購入馬鞍山「銀湖&middot;天峰」6座低層B室，成交呎價12,581元，廖所付的亦是首置印花稅。成交價較銀行估價低約16%至20%。<br />\n<br />\n發展局副秘麥成章 2600萬元首置購西半山單位<br />\n<br />\n另外，發展局副秘書長麥成章亦於本年11月初以首置名義簽置正式買賣合約，斥資2,650萬元購入西半山帝豪閣一伙千呎單位。據土地註冊處資料，帝豪閣C座低層2室，實用面積約1,196平方呎，三房間隔，連一個車位，成交價為2,650萬元，呎價約22,157元。<br />\n<br />\n新買家為麥成章及何美貞，二人英文名字分別為MAK SHING CHEUNG及HO MEI CHING FIONA，以聯名形式購入物業。前者與發展局副秘書長姓名相同，相信為同一人。"},{"pid":"9167f0e331e3c1719dbbc2417ded29cd1e50959a","tid":2329324,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6GK8ht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6GK8ht.png&h=82d6d1be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efc6ddcc8ea50ac4eae3c1701ff0acb9c2756e7e","tid":2329324,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyxUS8fr.gif&amp;h=670eec4a&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"908a721cd2df1b0258b547b5cb842de656b12a58","tid":2329324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bbbd1e870348a2e41c6a1cc80e5f605424c7892e","tid":2329324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"HK No IT"},{"pid":"7fe8ac1351264e05f4da3b558db52ed8efcc61ea","tid":2329324,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"糧照袋嘢鳩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n創科局長憤怒須為市民工作 建議港人放棄私隱權<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2350159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2350159</a>"}]}